For {= procurement_case =}+ Greek municipal bike-share procurement or contract cases, supply official public evidence for each of the {= lifecycle_facet =} required lifecycle facets per case, with {= event_stage =}+ high-confidence lifecycle stage and {= url =}+ URL for each facet. Each case needs one initiation record, one execution record, and one downstream record; each record's cited official URL must be the operative record or action for the facet and stage claimed in that record.

A procurement case can be a municipality's shared bicycle, e-bike sharing, or public micromobility system procurement, contract, implementation, amendment, or official operating-status case. Cases are open-set; do not try to prove that a municipality lacks a contract or turn search misses into absence claims. This is a public evidence ledger, not vendor ranking, outreach, procurement advice, implementation advice, legal analysis, compliance analysis, or sales targeting.

